      • classpath

        public static ClasspathConfigSource.Builder classpath​(String resource)
        Provides a Builder for creating a ConfigSource from the specified resource located on the classpath of the current thread's context classloader.

        The name of a resource is a '/'-separated full path name that identifies the resource. If the resource name has a leading slash then it is dropped before lookup.

        Parameters:
        resource - a name of the resource
        Returns:
        builder for a ConfigSource for the classpath-based resource
